<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>No Blogs Available - Yay for Peaceful Minds!</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(101, 116, 205, 0.05), rgba(155, 105, 200, 0.05));
        }

        .no-blogs-container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(101, 116, 205, 0.15);
            border-left: 5px solid #667eea;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .no-blogs-container:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(101, 116, 205, 0.2);
        }

        .cta-button {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #9f7aea);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
        }

        .cta-button::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -60%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: linear-gradient(to right,
                    rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.13) 0%,
                    rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.13) 77%,
                    rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5) 92%,
                    rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.0) 100%);
            transform: rotate(30deg);
        }

        .cta-button:hover::after {
            animation: shine 1.5s ease;
        }

        @keyframes shine {
            100% {
                left: 120%;
            }
        }

        .bounce {
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes bounce {

            0%,
            100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }

            50% {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4">
    <!-- Particles Background -->
    <div id="particles-js" class="fixed inset-0 pointer-events-none z-0"></div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl w-full">
        <div class="no-blogs-container p-8 md:p-10 text-center">
            <div class="message text-gray-800">
                <div class="bounce inline-block mb-6">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-16 w-16 text-indigo-500" fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5"
                            d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>

                <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-indigo-700">Hooray! No Overthinking Detected! üéâ
                </h1>

                <p class="text-xl mb-6 text-indigo-600">Looks like everyone's mind is peacefully quiet today. What a
                    wonderful feeling!</p>

                <div class="bg-indigo-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8 border border-indigo-100">
                    <p class="text-lg mb-4">‚ú® <span class="font-semibold">Celebrate this moment!</span> A calm mind is a
                        rare treasure in our busy world.</p>
                    <p class="text-lg">Enjoy this mental peace while it lasts - you've earned it!</p>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-8 text-left">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-center text-indigo-700">While You're Feeling Light...
                    </h2>
                    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                        <div class="bg-purple-50 p-5 rounded-lg">
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-purple-700 mb-2">üåº Things to Appreciate:</h3>
                            <ul class="space-y-2 text-purple-600">
                                <li class="flex items-start">
                                    <span class="mr-2">‚òï</span> That first sip of your favorite drink
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start">
                                    <span class="mr-2">üåû</span> Sunshine streaming through your window
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start">
                                    <span class="mr-2">üòå</span> The absence of that nagging "what if" thought
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-5 rounded-lg">
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-700 mb-2">üåà Happy Possibilities:</h3>
                            <ul class="space-y-2 text-blue-600">
                                <li class="flex items-start">
                                    <span class="mr-2">üìù</span> Write about something that makes you smile
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start">
                                    <span class="mr-2">üé®</span> Create something just for fun
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start">
                                    <span class="mr-2">üßò</span> Enjoy this rare overthinking-free moment
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="text-lg mb-8">If you do feel inspired to share some happy thoughts, we'd love to read them!
                    But no pressure - we're just glad you're feeling good. üòä</p>

                <div class="text-center">
                    <a href="/write"
                        class="cta-button inline-block text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg text-lg">
                        Share Some Joy
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 inline-block ml-1" viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                            fill="currentColor">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                                d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z"
                                clip-rule="evenodd" />
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/particles.js/2.0.0/particles.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        // Initialize non-interactive particles
        particlesJS("particles-js", {
            "particles": {
                "number": { "value": 50 },
                "color": { "value": "#9f7aea" },
                "shape": { "type": "circle" },
                "opacity": {
                    "value": 0.2,
                    "random": true,
                    "anim": { "enable": true, "speed": 1 }
                },
                "size": {
                    "value": 3,
                    "random": true,
                    "anim": { "enable": true, "speed": 2 }
                },
                "line_linked": {
                    "enable": true,
                    "distance": 150,
                    "color": "#9f7aea",
                    "opacity": 0.1,
                    "width": 1
                },
                "move": {
                    "enable": true,
                    "speed": 1,
                    "direction": "none",
                    "random": true
                }
            },
            "interactivity": {
                "detect_on": "canvas",
                "events": {
                    "onhover": { "enable": false },
                    "onclick": { "enable": false },
                    "resize": true
                }
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>

</html>